order to do a better job," he said.
</P>
<P>
He expressed the hope that CPPCC members will continue to
conduct studies and put forward more and better opinions and
suggestions.
</P>
<P>
Li attended a panel discussion by CPPCC members from circles
with no party affiliation, All-China Federation of Industry and
Commerce, Jiu San Society and the educational sector. 
</P>
