<HEADLINE> 2 Earthquakes Recorded by HK Observatory </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, March 4 (Xinhua) -- Two earthquakes, both measuring
6.5 on the Richter scale, hit southern Iran and the Celebes Sea
respectively, Hong Kong Observatory said here Thursday.
</P>
<P>
