<HEADLINE> Paris Stage Promoted to Golden League Series </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, March 4 (Xinhua) -- Paris has been added to the Golden
League series of elite athletics events, the IAAF announced on
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
International Amateur Athletic Federation president Primo
Nebiolo said the governing body had decided to add the Paris
meeting, but other details would be revealed later.
</P>
<P>
The French federation has been pressing for the Paris grand
prix meeting to be in the first tier of world events, which has
till now been limited to seven. 
</P>
</TEXT>
