<HEADLINE> Preparatory Meeting of NPC Session Held in Beijing -3 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Due to personnel changes in the leadership of five provincial
people's congresses, heads of these provincial delegations, namely
Cheng Weigao from Hebei, Zhang Dejiang from Jilin, Wang Maolin
from Hunan, Ruan Chongwu from Hainan and Yan Haiwang from Gansu,
have been replaced by Ye Liansong, Wang Yunkun, Yang Zhengwu, Du
Qinglin and Sun Ying, respectively.
</P>
<P>
Li Zhaochao, Chairman of the People's Government of the Guangxi
Zhuang Autonomous Region, and Gao Dezhan, Chairman of the
Agricultural and Rural Affairs Committee of the NPC Standing
Committee, were also made new members of the presidium.
</P>
