<HEADLINE> Romania Beats Estonia 2-0 in Soccer Friendly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, March 3 (Xinhua) -- International debutante Ionel
Ganea scored twice and Romania dominated Estonia 2-0 on Wednesday
in its first training match this year for European Championship
qualifying.
</P>
<P>
