parties in Kosovo to comply with the cease-fire and to try to make
the most of the remaining time for reaching a peace deal.
</P>
<P>
NATO Secretary General Javier Solana told the press that
compliance was a very important word between now and March 15, the
date set for the restart of the peace talks between the Yugoslav
authorities and the ethnic Albanians from the Yugoslav province of
Kosovo. (NATO-Kosovo)
</P>
