their monies in Africa when Africans themselves are not doing
it.
</P>
<P>
He suggested to investment promotion agencies, particularly,
foreign embassies, to effectively market investment opportunities
in the west African sub-region.
</P>
<P>
Kwaku further urged west African economies to take advantage of
the Information Technology and promote partnerships and
investment.
